From time to time you might experience problems with the syzygy.ca service. The tips below may help you get things going again without further intervention, but if not, please contact {{ Site.params.email }}
Restarting your Server Restarting your server can clear up a number of issues. If you see any of the following messages, please try restarting your server.
 500 internal server error, permissi9n failure checking authorization, I may need a new token  To restart your server, click on the Control panel button at the top right of the notebook.
